{"tid":604667,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"奴隸獸: 瑞士淫賤母親簽約做性奴　仲想將5歲女初夜獻主人","createTime":"2018-03-25T03:04:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-25T14:46:30.000Z","uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1ad0c34a731f148d7ea3e4161a330d586e3f3df9","tid":604667,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T03:04:55.000Z","msg":"聖加倫一名變態母親，與一名網上認識的德國男子簽下合約、奉對方為「主人」。她除了自願成為男子的性奴，更直播以性玩具虐待5歲女兒，還表示希望將女兒的初夜獻給「主人」。淫亂關係最終東窗事發，母親及男子分別被判囚4及5年，並禁止參與會接觸兒童的活動10年。 <br />\n<br />\n31歲變態巨乳母親莎拉（Sara I），和53歲德國男子海穆勒（Frank Heitmueller）簽下合約，內容寫道：「我願把身心獻給主人海穆勒，我是他的附屬品，除了我之外，我也會把我最愛的女兒獻給他。」莎拉之後透過視訊，用性玩具弄女兒下體；海穆勒則存下影像「欣賞」。 <br />\n<br />\n海穆勒的妻子偶然下在丈夫的電腦中發現變態短片，於是報警。案情指，海穆勒曾要求莎拉不要在網上說出女兒的名字，改以「小豬」作代號，以免被當局發現。莎拉在庭上表示，對自己的行為感到後悔；海穆勒則辯稱：「我是3個孩子的爸，並非孌童漢。」 <br />\n<br />\n然而，調查發現海穆勒曾把下體照傳給莎拉，莎拉則把照片拿給女兒看，還要求後「習慣他」。最終瑞士法院將莎拉判監4年3個月、海穆勒入獄5年；兩人在10年來不得參與能正常接觸兒童的活動，及須接受心理治療。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180325/photo/bknint-20180325000149824-0325_17011_001_01p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180325%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20180325000149824-0325_17011_001_01p.jpg&h=bc8e992a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 主人"},{"pid":"16034afd9d655071d1f0771d475761858d575df6","tid":604667,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T03:08:21.000Z","msg":"醜奴兒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef479fa439ece766b8c3d02dacc7ffcd23237bcd","tid":604667,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T03:09:53.000Z","msg":"cls<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fa231321e8534eb92b8df06d52c97c7b05e941d","tid":604667,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T03:11:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">    我絕對冇講過</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebc80bc1cd84e8b5f73dc49a4e30ba8d1d7a602f","tid":604667,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T03:33:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/25/113355_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F25%2F113355_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=fbdb4c05&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d9487ec19204cd3fc3ab7ec95501745bfafbc78f","tid":604667,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T14:46:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.makeagif.com/media/1-19-2018/fMhogb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.makeagif.com%2Fmedia%2F1-19-2018%2FfMhogb.gif&h=feb65084&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>亞冠盃 2018-04-04 20:00 傑志VS天津權健 @旺角大球場</strong></span><br />\n<em>*$100、$300門票已售罄，尚餘$250成人門票，欲購從速以免向隅</em><br />\n<br />\n<em><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">賽事門票將經由<span style=\"color: red;\">Cityline購票通之網站(<a href=\"http://www.cityline.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cityline.com&d=vYDgsfdcTD8A37J%2B7TckUcmDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=f2409be5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.cityline.com</a>)，門市及電話熱線(2111 5333) 公開發售至2018年4月3日晚上23時59分</span>，而預售之尚餘門票將會於比賽當日早上10時起於旺角大球場發售。有鑑於上年亞冠盃安排上的經驗，在與足總商討及建議下，比賽當日持<span style=\"color: red;\">主場門票入場的球迷，不論該主場門票屬任何種類，均必須出示有效之香港身份證明文件或非客隊所屬總會之護照方可進場。</span></span></em>"}]}